Package gw.api.assignment

Class AvailableQueues

java.lang.Object
gw.api.assignment.AvailableQueues
public class AvailableQueues extends Object
Wrapper object that contains the mapping of queues (ids) to number of activities and the list of available queues.

    • getQueues

      public AssignableQueue[] getQueues(AssignableQueue current)
      Returns:
      the non empty queues that are visible to the given user plus the given queue, all sorted in name order. If the given queue is null or already present in the list it is ignored. Otherwise it is included in the result array. May return empty array, but never null.

    • getBestQueue
